CINCINNATI, Ohio, Jan. 31.--Mr. Gerald Maxwell a member of the Wilson-Barrett DramatCompany, has been placed in the Cincinnati Sanitarium upon the certificate of a Cincinnati physician that he is insane. His hallucinations point to English politics and to a cipher for telegraphic messages which he has invented. View Full Article in Timesmachine Â»
